com.persistit

Class TreeStatistics

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.persistit.TreeStatistics

  • public class TreeStatistics
extends Object

    Collection of AtomicLong counters representing interesting statistics in a Tree. The store(byte[], int) and load(byte[], int, int) methods are designed to serialize and deserialize evolving versions of this class, therefore it is possible to add and remove new counters while remaining compatible with prior versions.

    Currently implemented counters include:

    • Fetch
    • Traverse
    • Store
    • Remove
